  "title": "sortBySelector not working anymore when set customRanking",
  "body": "Hi,\r\nI have setSetting my index to update customRanking field.\r\n\r\nI have updated from \r\n```\r\ncustomRanking: [\r\n            \"desc(best_offer.last_modified)\"\r\n        ],\r\n```\r\nTo\r\n```\r\ncustomRanking: [\r\n             \"desc(stock)\",\r\n             \"desc(created_on)\",\r\n             \"desc(last_modified)\"\r\n        ],\r\n```\r\nI have this parameters enable :\r\n```\r\nforwardToReplicas: true\r\n```\r\n\r\nMy initial index work great with this parameters but when i change the index with sortBySelector widget, it don't sort anymore  !\r\n\r\nI reverse to the original customRanking config but now it don't sort too...\r\n\r\nCould you help me please ?\r\n\r\n**Environment:**\r\n - I use the CDN version of algoliasearch : https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/algoliasearch/3/algoliasearch.min.js\r\n - Version instantsearch.min.js 2.10.3\r\n\r\nThanks",
